Class Employee

java.lang.Object
Employee
Direct Known Subclasses:
FullTime, PartTime
public class Employee
extends java.lang.Object
Employee is a class that creates a new Employee object. We take in a Profile, and contains the fields to store the profile as well as their payment. This class is used as the super class so that it works with FullTime and PartTime and Management.
Author:
Ashish Shenoy, Abimanyu Ananthu

      Parameters:
      employee - the employee we are checking the date agaisnt.
      Returns:
